  "title": "Chlorophyte armor",
  "summaries": [
    "<b>Chlorophyte armor</b> is a <linked>Hardmode</linked> <linked>armor</linked> set available after defeating all three <linked>mechanical bosses</linked>. It can be considered a partial upgrade of <linked>Hallowed armor</linked>, granting more <linked>defense</linked> and being geared more towards high <linked>ranged</linked> and <linked>magic</linked> damage output.",
    "Equipping the full set causes a <b>Leaf Crystal</b> to permanently appear over the player's head, automatically attacking enemies via a ranged projectile that costs no <linked>mana</linked> or <linked>ammunition</linked>.",
    "<ul><li>On the <linked>[img:Desktop version]</linked><linked> Desktop version</linked>, <linked>[img:Console version]</linked><linked> Console version</linked>, and <linked>[img:Mobile version]</linked><linked> Mobile version</linked>, the projectile is a bolt of energy that does instantaneous attacks to targets. It deals 100 base damage and inflicts a knockback of 10 <span>(Extremely strong)</span>.</li><li>On the <linked>[img:Old-gen console version]</linked><linked> Old-gen console version</linked>, <linked>Nintendo 3DS</linked><linked>[img:Nintendo 3DS version]</linked><linked> version</linked>, and <linked>[img:Legacy tModLoader version]</linked><linked> Legacy tModLoader version</linked>, the projectile is a green leaf that travels from the Leaf Crystal to the target. It deals <span class=\"eico i6\" title=\"Legacy tModLoader version\"><b></b><i></i></span> 100 / <span class=\"eico i3\" title=\"Old-gen console version\"><b></b><i></i></span> 50 / <span class=\"eico i5\" title=\"3DS version\"><b></b><i></i></span> 40 base damage and inflicts a knockback of <span class=\"eico i6\" title=\"Legacy tModLoader version\"><b></b><i></i></span> 10 <span>(Extremely strong)</span> / <span class=\"eico i3 i5\" title=\"Old-gen console and 3DS versions\"><b></b><i></i></span> 5 <span>(Average)</span>.</li></ul>",
    "A full set of Chlorophyte armor requires 54 <linked>Chlorophyte Bars</linked>, or <span class=\"eico i1 i2 i4\" title=\"Desktop, Console and Mobile versions\"><b></b><i></i></span> 270 / <span class=\"eico i3 i5 i6\" title=\"Old-gen console, 3DS and Legacy tModLoader versions\"><b></b><i></i></span> 324 <linked>Chlorophyte Ore</linked>. Crafting the full set with every helmet type requires 78 bars (<span class=\"eico i1 i2 i4\" title=\"Desktop, Console and Mobile versions\"><b></b><i></i></span> 390 / <span class=\"eico i3 i5 i6\" title=\"Old-gen console, 3DS and Legacy tModLoader versions\"><b></b><i></i></span> 468 ore)."
  ],
